# Task 6 – Create Business Schedule

## Project

**Virtual Agent–Driven SLA Breach Awareness & Justification System**

---

## Objective

This task creates a Business Schedule that defines the official working hours of the IT Support team. The schedule is used by ServiceNow SLAs to calculate response and resolution times only during business hours.

---

## Navigation

**System Scheduler → Schedules → New**

---

## Configuration Details

| Field         | Value                     |
| ------------- | ------------------------- |
| Schedule Name | IT Support Business Hours |
| Time Zone     | IST (Asia/Kolkata)        |
| Working Days  | Monday–Friday             |
| Working Hours | 09:00 AM – 06:00 PM       |
| Show As       | Busy                      |

---

## Steps Completed

* Created Business Schedule
* Configured Schedule Entries
* Set Working Days
* Set Business Hours
* Configured Repeat Pattern
* Saved the Schedule

---

## Deliverables

* Business Schedule Configuration
* Schedule Entry Configuration
* Implementation Documentation
* Screenshots

---

## Expected Result

The Business Schedule is successfully configured and ready to be used by ServiceNow Service Level Agreements for accurate business-hour-based SLA calculations.

---

## Status

**Completed**

